desc.html: This is a map depicting the local government quarters or neighbourhoods into which Nicosia is divided, but only those within the walls. The base map is of 1930s Nicosia, with the rough boundaries drawn over the street map by the author of this file after consulting various sources.

wiki.Credit:
Map of 1930's Nicosia is out of copyright (pub.c.1940). Boundaries drawn by myself after consulation with (amongst others): "Population Enumerated by Sex, Age, District, Municipality/Community and Quarter, 2011" Census of the Republic of Cyprus; 6th edition of the publication “Statistical Codes of Municipalities, Communities and Quarters of Cyprus” (both publ.by Statistical Service of Republic of Cyprus); Google Maps August 2013; Nicosia Municipality powerpoint presentation (A.M. Hadjilyra Jan 2004), retrieved Feb 2013
Previously published: Created here for the first time merely as a pictorial aid for readers of the Wikipedia article on NIcosia
